---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base
  title="About, atomic"
  description="What atomic is, why it exists, and how the writing here is sourced and edited."
>
  <article class="container container--narrow about">
    <header class="about-header">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>A blog about habits, without the fluff.</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        <strong>atomic</strong> is a blog about building better habits and breaking bad ones. The
        writing here aims for one thing: to be the most useful piece on its topic that you read
        this week.
      </p>

      <h2>What you'll find</h2>
      <p>
        Practical, research-backed guides on behaviour change, habit stacking, habit tracking,
        identity-based habits, routines, and the books worth reading on each. Plain English, short
        sentences, no hype.
      </p>

      <h2>How the writing is sourced</h2>
      <p>
        Every non-obvious claim is tied to a named source, peer-reviewed research, recognised
        books, or expert practitioners. Quotes are verbatim and linked. If we can't source it, we
        don't claim it.
      </p>

      <h2>What you won't find</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Motivational filler dressed up as advice.</li>
        <li>Fabricated personal anecdotes.</li>
        <li>Hustle-culture clichés.</li>
        <li>Third-party trackers beyond basic, privacy-respecting analytics.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Start reading</h2>
      <p>
        New here? <a href="/blog/how-to-build-habits-that-stick/">Start with the foundational guide</a>,
        or <a href="/tags/">browse by topic</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <style>
    .about {
      padding-top: var(--space-7);
      padding-bottom: var(--space-9);
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .about { padding-top: var(--space-8); }
    }
    .about-header {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-7);
    }
    .eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    }
    .about-header h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: var(--step-4);
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      max-width: 22ch;
    }
  </style>
</Base>
